-No. Don't make that face.
-No. But...

2396
01:46:57.625 --> 01:46:59.905
-It's not a big deal. It's...
-You wanted to be friends?

2397
01:46:59.958 --> 01:47:02.041
Yes. well. it's obviously
too late now. isn't it?

2398
01:47:03.208 --> 01:47:04.041
