I'm gonna take you somewhere.

2422
01:48:08.833 --> 01:48:10.184
and it's gonna be a transformation.

2423
01:48:10.208 --> 01:48:11.208
-All right.
-All right.

2424
01:48:11.291 --> 01:48:13.500
-Thank you so much.
-Oh. um. I don't know...

2425
01:48:13.583 --> 01:48:15.125
No. they are. I ordered them.

2426
